description:
I've been having a lot of fun playing this game recently and decided to make a short LP for it.

I figure we will keep going until we either die, or the game gets repetitive. However, a couple basic goals are to make it to Day 30, and to research everything in the game.

Game Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/219740/
